APIs.Description:
AeroDataBox API is an aviation API with useful and unique features for your aviation-related application.
This includes:
Aircrafts API:
search by registration;
aircraft image recognition based on computer vision (BETA);
search aircraft photo (BETA).
Airports API:
search by IATA/ ICAO codes;
airport local time;
airport delay statistics and delay index;
airport flights arrivals and departures board + schedules (FIDS);
airport runways;
airport routes and daily flights statistics;
airport current runways in use (soon).
Flights API:
flight schedules;
flight live tracking and updates;
flight delay statistics.
API IS CURRENTLY UNDER ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT AND MANY FEATURES ARE NOT YET RELEASED OR IN BETA STAGE RIGHT NOW.

Synapsify’s REST API is based on a core set of linguistic algorithms, utilizing phonemics, natural language processing (NLP), machine learning, etc. The API has been designed to be as flexible as possible, and can be adapted to a very wide range of domains and fields of interest, including:
Reading any type of written content based on several dimensions;
Revealing the quality, balance, credibility and quotablity of such content and its most important topics and phrases;
Indexing and matching against other written content or customized indexes;
Enhancing the ability to discover, understand and segment actionable insights.

Getting balance of bitcoin and in fiat via API is done by sending an http POST to https://bips.me/api/v1/getbalance
On a successful POST a JSON encoded array will be received in the response. On any invalid API request, an error message will be received in the response of the POST. Your system should account for this.

API key should never be publicly visible. If compromised, one can generate a new one in BIPS account.
